headline.main: China's Xi Says Shanghai Should Lead in Reform, Innovation: Xinhua
headline.print_headline: China's Xi Says Shanghai Should Lead in Reform, Innovation: Xinhua

lead_paragraph: Shanghai should lead China's plans to reform and advance innovation, the official Xinhua news agency has reported President Xi Jinping as saying at the annual meeting of parliament.
